<CD-RAT><Entry><HWD>PRON</HWD><Activity><VoiceRecorder layer="1" h="460" w="670" y="10" x="10"><Title alignment="left" isOn="1">Expressing surprise and disbelief<br /></Title><Instruction alignment="left" isOn="1"><FONT FACE="Verdana">Click to listen, then record and playback the woman’s sentences.</FONT><br /></Instruction><ReferenceObject soundIsOn="0" videoIsOn="0" defaultHeight="200" alignment="left" isOn="0" /><ScrollableAssets /><Content><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>1. Look, I really do want to go on holiday with you.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="1" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    You could’ve fooled me.</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="2" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>2. Jo wants to run the Dublin marathon the day after the London one.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="3" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    That’s ridiculous!</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="4" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>3. Susie’s left her job at the supermarket.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="5" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    I’m not surprised.</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="6" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>4. Freddie’s been offered a car with his new job.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="7" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    Really?</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="8" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>5. Rob says he’ll be here on time tonight.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="9" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    I’ll believe that when I see it.</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="10" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>6. Kate’s just been given a grant to set up her new business.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="11" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    That’s fantastic!</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="12" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>7. Of course, if Eve’s husband doesn’t come to the cinema, then neither will Eve.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="13" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    Obviously.</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="14" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>8. Jorgen is a very nervous passenger after his car accident last year.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="15" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    I’m not surprised.</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="16" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>9. I’m going to do a watercolour painting course in Italy for two weeks.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="17" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>    That’s brilliant!</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="18" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question><Question><Score num="1" /><ReferenceText1>10. I’m late home because I didn’t finish work until 10 p.m.</ReferenceText1><ListenButton id="19" url="" linkType="Sound" /><ReferenceText2>     Do you seriously expect me to believe that?</ReferenceText2><ListenButton2 id="20" url="" linkType="Sound" /><AudioRecorder /></Question></Content></VoiceRecorder><Feedback playallOn="1" showAnswersOn="1" animatedFeedbackOn="1" testModeOn="0" instantFeedbackOn="0"><Sounds /></Feedback><GenericActivity hintsNextTo="0" timerIsOn="0" CDPrefsFolder="xml/" CDPrefsFile="cd.xml"><ActivityCanvas graphicAlpha="100" folder="" file="" colourAlpha="100" colour="transparent" /><SoundLibrary y="10" x="10" isOn="0"><Item bDefault="1" endTime="2.9" startTime="0" duration="2.9" id="1" file="06105101.mp3" folder="audio/" /><Item endTime="1.57" startTime="0" duration="1.57" id="2" file